---
import Icon from './Icon.astro';
---

<section class="box skills">
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="code" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h5> üìä Data analysis</h5>
		<p style="text-align: justify;">Data analysis and wrangling with Python, R and Stata. Management of relational databases with MySQL. Data collection with Kobo Toolbox, Open Data Kit, Survey Solution.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="terminal-window" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h5> üó∫Ô∏è Reporting</h5>
		<p style="text-align: justify;">Creation of dashboards using Power BI and Tableau++ to monitor performance indicators (KPIs), monitoring, evaluation, analysis of survey data.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="terminal-window" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h5>üíª Modeling/research</h5>
		<p style="text-align: justify;">Developing econometrics model in social science and research, Panels data, logistic regression, Economic modelling, time series, sales forecasting and machine learning.</p>
